&lt;h2 id=&#34;data-visualization-common-ways-people-have-died&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#data-visualization-common-ways-people-have-died&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Data Visualization - Common Ways People Have Died&lt;/h2&gt;
